  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599205743010-YNJ09DD15E037PHYHN2P/4a-album3031515_600x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>The fact that <a href=\"http://bit.ly/1gcs75O\">Two Peas in a Bucket</a> got an advanced shipment of 12 SKU's for my latest collection with American Crafts is a huge plus. There's a <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/146845-plus-one-amy-tangerine-cloth-screenprinted-live-the-life-you-love-d-ring-12x12-album/\">12x12 D-ring fabric album</a> with the quote you see above. As you probably already know, my collaboration with American Crafts, Plus One, included another collaboration within it, with <a href=\"http://kalbarteski.bigcartel.com/\">Kal Barteski</a>. She is an amazingly talented artist and she's even sharing her knowledge for those interested in learning brush script in an online class called <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/shop/classrooms/life-scripted?aff=6cc2c70f\">Life | Scripted. </a>In case you missed it, <a href=\"https://amy-tan-z6av.squarespace.com/amy-tangerine/2013/12/1.html\">here's the post</a> where I announced the new collection. Though there was just a limited time to create some samples for the catalog, I went to town and fell in love with so many of the products.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599205759493-DY2YLCQ6OT6D0O4HUEUU/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599205770230-SQITB8CBZ8WNCZU5RFIG/4c-DSC_3264-600x426.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>One of my favorite items has to be <a href=\"http://bit.ly/KxMJvv\">these awesome foam phrase stickers with Kal Barteski's script</a>. I want to stick them on pretty much everything.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599205786516-6GZG5M6OPS27FTP1YKVA/4d-TwinsThickers.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>And washi lovers this one is for you - <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/146844-plus-one-amy-tangerine-mixtape/\">Mixtape</a> is here &amp; this time we have 6 super skinny rolls of washi tape in one pack. YAY!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599205808622-EXXRUQZTOJALGRFOHIQ2/4e-washi-3031514_600x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Hope you're loving what you see so far of <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/_plus%2520one_/_amy_tangerine_/%3Favad%3D41735_c5c0e2ad\">Plus One</a>!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
